title: Baby Frog ECO: Compostable Tableware
description:
Going live on June 2nd! only on Kickstarter! Please support us!
Baby Frog ECO is a children's tableware, 100% safe, compostable, and harmless to the environment and people. It is made from eggshell and vegetable oils. We aim to influence a future where we can eliminate petroleum derivatives, plastics, and additives.
